{"tid":1344402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點先可以令政府回應五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-21T22:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:28:31.000Z","uid":43103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"34d855a78815022c836ed2d8cd5edbdb0fc4f870","tid":1344402,"uid":43103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:28:12.000Z","msg":"經過琴晚一役，小弟有啲意見想講下，如果有講錯請大家屌醒我<br />\n<br />\n我喺琴晚其中一個喺西環發夢嘅人，留意到啲警犬冇好似之前咁追住我吔嚟打，當然喺我哋人多，夠團結嘅關係。<br />\n<br />\n但喺我有聽紀律部隊嘅朋友（唔喺警犬）講過，佢哋比人影到打人都喺要孭飛，所以依家先改變策略打持久戰，我哋唔郁，佢吔都唔會點樣追打我吔，會慢慢包圍我哋逼我哋走。不過我覺得只供參考。<br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊其實如果我吔淨係齋同班警犬對峙（唔喺鼓吹大家去衝）冇一個特定目的，到最後都會比狗包圍，大家都喺要撤退。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣其實我哋仲有咩可以做呢？和理非遊行政府冇理，發夢又冇理。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">遊行發夢我都會照去</span></span>，我只喺希望討論一下行動可以向邊方面升級，先可以令政府回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bbd95125abc1c427ea8cc32ccae7da5e2936e0","tid":1344402,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:30:14.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 寫咗個白宮聯署<br />\nrequest國際人道救援/援助<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fe81467b1d1922e0e82bd2457c43c8e5937610d4","tid":1344402,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:33:10.000Z","msg":"到而家都仲未醒呀你<br />\n佢唔會理你死架"},{"pid":"7e3c8e70e177b9c00c582f11b8a56af9051b0d3c","tid":1344402,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:33:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人要